The paper focuses on learning image classifiers, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses learning mechanisms and models, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions using visual analogy, which is related to natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category. Finally, the paper proposes a new method for learning classifiers, which could also be related to neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
